OL,3,CHomeless given 'confidence boost' with
OL,4,Cfree haircuts
OL,6,FA homeless man has thanked college
OL,7,Fstudents who cut his hair for free -
OL,8,Fand says he feels "smashing" after the
OL,9,Fchop.
OL,11,FThe barbering students, from ,
OL,12,FLancashire, welcomed members of the
OL,13,Fcommunity to Burnley's 'Church on the
OL,14,FStreet'.
OL,16,FAs well as providing free haircuts to
OL,17,Fthe homeless, the students were also
OL,18,Fgiven a chance to practice their
OL,19,Fcommunication skills too.
