OL,3,CHomeless given 'confidence boost' with
OL,4,Cfree haircuts
OL,6,FDerek, who is homeless and one of
OL,7,Fthose happy to get a pampered, said:
OL,8,F"I feel great, it's smashing - I feel
OL,9,Fa lot better now".
OL,11,FTwo of the students taking part,
OL,12,FMelissa and Jess, think the scheme is
OL,13,Fa great way of giving back to those
OL,14,Fwho may be struggling.
OL,16,FJess said: "With price rises it's not
OL,17,Feasy, and it's becoming a luxury and
OL,18,Fwe just want to help people out. It is
OL,19,Fnice to be able to make people's days."
