OL,3,CHomeless given 'confidence boost' with
OL,4,Cfree haircuts
OL,6,FGetting a haircut can boost anyone's
OL,7,Fwellbeing and confidence, but is a
OL,8,Fluxury that is not normally an option
OL,9,Fafforded to those living on the
OL,10,Fstreets.
OL,12,Ffrom said: "It's like two fold, you
OL,13,Fhaven't had to spend 10 quid, but it
OL,14,Fmakes such a difference.
OL,16,F"With a new haircut they smile, so you
OL,17,Fcan see it's worth far more than
OL,18,Fhaving your haircut."
