OL,3,CHomeless given 'confidence boost' with
OL,4,Cfree haircuts
OL,6,FThe students and the group of homeless
OL,7,Fpeople in Burnley are hoping this will
OL,8,Fbecome a more regular service.
OL,10,F, which is a registered charity set up
OL,11,Fby veteran hairdresser Stewart Roberts
OL,12,Falso provides free cuts for those on
OL,13,Fthe streets.
OL,15,FThe charity says hairdressers have a
OL,16,Fknown empathy and are great
OL,17,Fcommunicators.
