OL,3,CHomeless given 'confidence boost' with
OL,4,Cfree haircuts
OL,6,FThe industry is known for its
OL,7,Fgenerosity and willingness to help
OL,8,Fpeople therefore there are many that
OL,9,Fwould willingly give some of their
OL,10,Ftime and expertise.
OL,12,FIt says there is something very
OL,13,Fpersonal about cutting someone's hair
OL,14,Fthat can be both enjoyable and
OL,15,Ftherapeutic which is something that
OL,16,Fmany homeless people rarely get.
OL,18,FIt may be "just a haircut", but it's
OL,19,Fthe kindness shown that makes a
OL,20,Fhomeless person know that people
OL,21,F"really care".
